  "text": "In the seminal papers by Alon and Stav [CITATION_1] 7] and by Axenovich, Kézdy and Martin [CITATION_2] , the fundamental question was the maximum distance of a graph G on n vertices from hereditary property H . In fact, the maximum distance is asymptotically the same as that of the Erdős-Rényi random graph G(n, p), for some value of p. 2 Colored regularity graphs",
